body:
{{sticker:zombie-nunu-bummed}} 
As a faithful Ezreal main since the days of S6, I get annoyed when some people *cough* Necrit *cough* look at Ez the wrong way - as a sociopath who remorselessly KILLS (wut) and has no feelings.{{sticker:sg-ahri-1}} {{sticker:zombie-brand-mindblown}} 
As such, I would like if we get an Ez story where instead of him writing it, it is in his head and thoughts, showing his good nature as opposed to the glorified self he tries to write up to be more famous in order to have his parents come back.{{sticker:sg-ezreal}}
